Name: Prime
About: Prime is a new, intuitive & powerful DeFi ecosystem designed to safely keep your tron hard at work for passive and sustainable growth indefinitely. Behaving like a dapp-fund, Prime diversifies itself across several dapp & game ecosystems to safely provide sustainable growth for your tron, all whilst you still keep access to your deposit. Using Prime is simple, upon depositing your portfolio is handled autonomously by the contract giving you peace of mind.
Fees: Because Prime diversifies itself across several dapp & game ecosystems players inherit said dapp fees. These are one-off (typically called entry & exit fees) and amounts to roughly 20% of deposits. Early players also pay a platform fee on deposits to support development, this is set to 1% for launch but will decrease to 0% over time. Finally borrowing is completely free though players who have outstanding borrowing on their deposit take a small 5% penalty on their divs (which goes back into the dapps).
